channel.title: Clean 06 Server/Client?
channel.description:
Hello everyone,
For the past week I was searching with some co-workers about some "clean" server/client source code. This is because we want to start working in one, I know there's some really good servers about to open and some of them already open, but we still want to make one...
I was searching and testing serveral 06 Source servers/clients but I din't find any of them "clean", I was working with one for 1 month, I quit because was too buggy and I knew that I could find another one better... Well, I guess I was wrong, so I don't know if someone could help me... There's a good 06 Source to work?
Sorry about my bad english in advance, I'm trying my best.
Thank you, Dave.
